# Monorepo and CI Safeguards

- Use pnpm workspace filters for app dependencies:
  - `pnpm --filter customer-web add ...`
  - `pnpm --filter order-service add ...`
- Do not install app dependencies in workspace root by default.
- Keep runtime versions aligned: `.nvmrc`, `engines`, CI Node version.
- CI checks must include lint, type-check, test, build.

## Reliability Rules

- Avoid wildcard package names (e.g. `@radix-ui/react-*`).
- Pin infra images (Kafka/Postgres/Redis/Meilisearch), avoid `latest`.
- Prefer `docker compose` command syntax.
